WEBVTT

00:02:57.269 --> 00:03:01.220
Benki ya Dunia ina kipimo kinachotwa
"Mazingira ya Kufanya Biashara,"

00:03:01.244 --> 00:03:04.281
ambacho hulinganisha urahisi
au ugumu wa kuanzisha biashara

00:03:04.305 --> 00:03:05.902
katika nchi yoyote.

00:03:05.926 --> 00:03:07.545
Na kama unavyofikiria,

00:03:08.404 --> 00:03:12.025
kuanzisha au kuendesha biashara
katika nchi ambayo serikali ni mgonjwa --

00:03:12.049 --> 00:03:13.498
karibia haiwezekani.

00:03:14.432 --> 00:03:18.156
Rais wa Kenya alijua hili,
hivyo mwaka 2014,

00:03:18.180 --> 00:03:21.549
alikuja katika maabara yetu na kuomba tushirikiane naye

00:03:21.573 --> 00:03:24.843
kuisaidia Kenya katika ukuaji wa biashara.

00:03:25.689 --> 00:03:27.411
Aliweka lengo kuu:

00:03:27.778 --> 00:03:32.700
alitaka Kenya kuwa kati ya nchi 50 za juu katika kipimo hiki cha Benki ya Dunia.